<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Registration Page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: stretch;
            min-height: 100vh;
            max-height: 610px;
            background: url(/Images/register1.jpg) no-repeat center center fixed; /* Full background picture */
            background-size: cover;
        }

        .left-side {
            flex: 1;
            background-image: url('');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            text-align: center;

        }

        .right-side {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: right;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0px;
            margin-left:600px;
            margin-top:20px;
        }

        .registration-form {
            max-width: 1200px; /* Increased max-width */
            padding: 50px; /* Increased padding */
            background-color: rgba(52, 73, 94, 0.7); /* Form background color with opacity */
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin: auto;
        }

            .registration-form h2 {
                text-align: center;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                color: white;
                font-weight: bold;
            }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: white;
        }

            .form-group label {
                display: inline-block; /* Changed display property */
                font-weight: bold;
                margin-bottom: 5px;
                color: white;
            }

            .form-group input {
                width: 100%;
                padding: 10px;
                border: 1px solid #ccc;
                border-radius: 5px;
                color: black;
            }

        .btn-primary {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            background: #34495e;
            background: #388e3c;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            color: #fff;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

            .btn-primary:hover {
                background-color: #0056b3;
            }

        .form-footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .form-footer a {
                text-decoration: none;
                color: #007bff;
            }

                .form-footer a:hover {
                    text-decoration: underline;
                }

        .left-side h3 {
            /* Add styles for the h3 heading */
            text-align: center;
            color: #34495e; /* Example color */
            font-size: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-style: italic;
            font-family: Constantia, "Lucida Bright", "DejaVu Serif", Georgia, serif;
            color: #295f4e;
        }

        .left-side p {
            /* Add styles for the paragraph */
            font-size: 22px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: white; /* Example color */
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px;
            background-color: rgba(52, 73, 94, 0.5);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: -30px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-family: Constantia, "Lucida Bright", "DejaVu Serif", Georgia, serif;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="left-side">

        @*<div class="left-side"><h3>Clean, Green, Serene: Where Apartment Living Meets Peace of Mind...!</h3></div>
        <div class="left-side"><p>Welcome to our apartment cleaning scheduling system! Say goodbye to the hassle of organizing cleaning rotations. With our intuitive shift calendar, you can easily assign yourself to flexible cleaning shifts within the rotation, ensuring that every corner of the apartment gets the attention it deserves. 
            Keep track of the cleaning progress effortlessly, as everyone can monitor the cleaning status and contribute to maintaining a pristine living space. Our platform promotes transparency and accountability, allowing for seamless coordination among residents. Join us in fostering a clean and comfortable environment for all!</p></div>*@

    </div>
    <div class="right-side">
        <div class="registration-form">
            <h2>Register</h2>
            <form action="/Home/RegisterUser" method="post">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="name">Name</label>
                    <input type="text" id="Full_Name" name="Full_Name" placeholder="Enter your name">
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="name">Phone Number</label>
                    <input type="text" id="Contact_No" name="Contact_No" placeholder="Enter your mobile number">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="email">Email</label>
                    <input type="email" id="Email" name="Email" placeholder="Enter your email">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="password">Password</label>
                    <input type="password" id="Password" name="Password" placeholder="Enter your password">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="confirm_password">Confirm Password</label>
                    <input type="password" id="confirm_password" name="confirm_password" placeholder="Confirm your password">
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">Register</button>
                <div class="form-footer">

                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script>
        $(document).ready(function () {
            // Event handler for the register button
            $('#registerBtn').click(function () {
                // Navigate to the registration page
                window.location.href = '/Register'; // Replace 'RegistrationPageUrl' with the actual URL of your registration page
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>


